sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebUI as Angular UI
    participant AgentService as Agent Service
    participant NATS as NATS JetStream
    participant ControlPlane as Control Plane
    participant Container as Agent Container
    participant Orchestrator as Orchestrator Agent
    participant Agents as Specialist Agents
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Chat Start Flow
    User->>WebUI: Start new chat<br/>(select GitHub repo or none)
    WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit<br/>{message, repository_id}
    AgentService->>PostgreSQL: Create thread
    PostgreSQL-->>AgentService: Thread created
    
    AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.start<br/>{run_id, user_id, task, project_id, repository_id, ...}
    NATS-->>AgentService: Published
    
    NATS->>ControlPlane: Deliver start message
    ControlPlane->>ControlPlane: Get repository details
    ControlPlane->>Container: Create container with env vars<br/>(RUN_ID, USER_ID, TASK, etc.)
    Container->>Container: Clone repository
    Container->>Container: Start worker process
    Container->>Container: Auto-start workflow from env vars
    ControlPlane->>PostgreSQL: Save ChatContainer record
    ControlPlane-->>NATS: ACK
    
    AgentService-->>WebUI: Chat started
    WebUI-->>User: Display chat interface

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Agent Execution Flow
    User->>WebUI: Send task message
    WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit<br/>{message, trigger_workflow: true}
    AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.start<br/>{run_id, user_id, task, ...}
    NATS-->>AgentService: Published
    
    NATS->>ControlPlane: Deliver start message
    ControlPlane->>Container: Create/recreate container
    Container->>Orchestrator: Auto-start orchestrator agent
    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Analyze task
    
    loop Agent sequence execution
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.scouting
        NATS->>AgentService: State update (global stream)
        AgentService->>PostgreSQL: Update chat state
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Scouting repository"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: repo-scout agent
        Agents->>Container: Read repository files
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Repository summary
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.planning
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Planning solution"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: skills-lead agent
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Selected agents
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: solution-planner agent
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Implementation plan
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.designing
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Designing solution"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: Design agent
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Design spec
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.implementing
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Implementing"
        
        par Parallel implementation
            Orchestrator->>Agents: Go developer
            Agents->>Container: Write/patch files
        and
            Orchestrator->>Agents: Angular developer
            Agents->>Container: Write/patch files
        and
            Orchestrator->>Agents: DevOps developer
            Agents->>Container: Write/patch files
        end
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.testing
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Testing"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: Test engineers
        Agents->>Container: Run tests
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Test results
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.reviewing
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Reviewing code"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: Code reviewer
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Review results
        
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.verifying
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show "Verifying completion"
        
        Orchestrator->>Agents: Completion verifier
        Agents-->>Orchestrator: Verification result
        
        alt Verification passed
            Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.completed
            NATS->>AgentService: State update
            AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
            WebUI->>User: Show "Task completed"
        else Verification failed
            Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.repairing
            NATS->>AgentService: State update
            AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
            WebUI->>User: Show "Repairing issues"
            Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Increment repair count
            Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Return to implementing
        end
    end
    
    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Human Intervention Flow
    alt Protected action detected
        Orchestrator->>NATS: Publish state<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.waiting_approval
        NATS->>AgentService: State update
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE event
        WebUI->>User: Show approval dialog
        
        User->>WebUI: Approve or reject
        WebUI->>AgentService: POST /approvals/{id}/approve
        AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.resume
        NATS->>ControlPlane: Deliver resume message
        ControlPlane->>Container: Recreate container
        Container->>Orchestrator: Resume execution from checkpoint
    end

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Chat Termination Flow
    User->>WebUI: Close chat
    WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit/close/{chat_id}
    AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.close<br/>{run_id}
    NATS-->>AgentService: Published
    
    NATS->>ControlPlane: Deliver close message
    ControlPlane->>Container: Stop container
    Container->>Container: Cleanup resources
    ControlPlane->>Container: Remove container
    ControlPlane->>PostgreSQL: Update ChatContainer status
    ControlPlane-->>NATS: ACK
    
    NATS->>AgentService: Message delivered
    AgentService-->>WebUI: Chat closed
    WebUI-->>User: Chat terminated
